summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 66W, page 159, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Columbia Addition, Lots 21-40, inclusive, Block 2, and Lots 41-60, inclusive, Block 4, located on both sides of Americus St. between 39th Ave. So. and 42nd Ave. So., as Duplex Residence High Density (RD 5000) Zone.
